comments.body:
I spawned 5 containers simultaneously using goroutines, seemed to work just fine for me on v2.0.4. Of course, this worked fine in the case of only 2 containers as well.

@sunyitao I see that you're using the podman from container-tools module on centos which is often very old. Can you check if the podman from OBS has this issue as well? Instructions for fetching it can be found at https://podman.io/getting-started/installation .

@mheon @vrothberg hope it's fair to close this. Please reopen if not :)
